=== WIND_CHIME_GARDEN ===
# id: 78
# title: The Wind Chime Garden
# chinese_title: 风铃花园
# category: Shrine
# mode: dungeon

Hundreds of wind chimes hang from the ceiling of a vast atrium, ringing in harmonious patterns despite the still air. Each chime is inscribed with a radical. The sound washes over you in waves, and you feel your mind sharpening with each resonant tone.

* [Listen to the chimes and absorb the lesson]
  ~ gain_radical("风")
  "风" (fēng) — wind, style, manner
* [Strike a specific chime to hear its tone]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "铃" (líng) — bell, chime
* [Take a chime as a memento]
  ~ gain_item("neural_boost")
  "念" (niàn) — to remember, memento
* [Rest in the garden's peaceful atmosphere]
  ~ heal(10)
  "静" (jìng) — quiet, serene
